{"tid":1095531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪亞高哥斯達涉嫌屌自己老母   被判紅牌離場","createTime":"2019-04-07T05:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T09:34:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":135,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"114df437442c18be8f710294ac2800f2f91f4df4","tid":1095531,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.sportsyeah.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/66758D47-171A-42AF-8712-A34BA4CB18DA.jpeg?w=680\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.sportsyeah.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F66758D47-171A-42AF-8712-A34BA4CB18DA.jpeg%3Fw%3D680&h=f896f7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德里體育會前鋒迪亞高哥斯達（Diego Costa）在昨夜對巴塞隆拿一戰涉嫌辱罵球證而被判離場。馬體會已經決定就DC的紅牌提出上訴，原因竟然是DC當時沒有辱罵球證，他是因為懊悔自己的犯規而咒罵自己。<br />\n<br />\n在比賽28分鐘，DC在一次犯規之後與球證口角，隨後被直接紅牌罰下，DC自己想要解釋，但是卻根本無濟於事。根據一開始西班牙各大媒體的說法，DC很可能說的是「la puta madre que te pari&oacute;」(X)，而這確實足以讓球證罰他離場。<br />\n<br />\n但是Cardena Ser電台的現場記者從馬體會更衣室得到的消息指，DC方面否認自己辱罵球證，他當時說的是「la puta madre que me pari&oacute;」(我呢個XX老母生嘅仔)，因為球員很懊悔自己之前的犯規動作，但是代詞me卻被錯聽成了第二人稱的te。而賽後球證報告出現另一個版本：DC對球證喊的是「me cago en tu puta madre」（我X你老母）<br />\n<br />\n而根據轉播商Movistar+的鏡頭顯示，DC的口型更像是me，而不是te。"},{"pid":"82eb4e9cca5446cf36732739d56e73fb9b6d42a6","tid":1095531,"uid":10576,"like":2,"dislike":31,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"球證話係就係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6163d875455a3891c23965a6fd255ac4ef8f8b","tid":1095531,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261f9bf667c54a1c6337a279c862d2228e6f3d43","tid":1095531,"uid":159086,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"咒罵自己就得?死臭口 抵你死啦"},{"pid":"ff3d3ffcf899add7cc7030c58eee2bb16ad59d2f","tid":1095531,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"球證話係咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f65f610a833ba486cc902225427cc77759c1a08","tid":1095531,"uid":36372,"like":166,"dislike":2,"score":164,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"邊有人會踢波屌自己老母架"},{"pid":"2d12d26d89425a9737b617811c6bd57fb5bb7ec0","tid":1095531,"uid":34419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"屌自己老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑咗"},{"pid":"609e1a49f515fc0bc8270c8db32247f29f83a13c","tid":1095531,"uid":1423,"like":128,"dislike":0,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"係球證面前屌自己老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罰你出去睇精神科"},{"pid":"c12e74f845d71699ff65365cc585679c4db66a80","tid":1095531,"uid":155902,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"呢個理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢成個動作衝住去球證講ga wor<br />\n懊悔會唔會衝埋去睥住球證講屌自己老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f3fb0dd01698822c99f59faf3c5fa92f54e041","tid":1095531,"uid":23749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f65f610a833ba486cc902225427cc77759c1a08","tid":1095531,"uid":36372,"like":166,"dislike":2,"score":164,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"邊有人會踢波屌自己老母架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"大把啦 益不如益自己<img src=\"